snippet.title: Rising Lords – Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching!
Medieval Turn-Based Stragy Game Rising Lords will release in 2019. 

Find more infos or wishlist the game on https://store.steampowered.com/app/835650/rising_lords
Follow our progress with daily updates on http://Twitter.com/Argonwood
Or visit us on  https://argonwood.com


Music:
'Folk Round' by Kevin MacLeod (incompetech.com) 
Licensed under Creative Commons: By Attribution 3.0
http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/3.0/
additional instruments, editing and arrangement by Hendrik Dingler (http://www.hendrikdingler.de)

Video composition: Nikita Musatov (http://keeveegames.net/)
